    dc:description "Figure 53. Uvariopsis citrata Couvreur & Niang A trunk with flower buds B leaves, upper side C leaf base, lower side D lear apex, upper side E leaf base, upper side F female flower bud, two petals removed, side view G male flower bud, one petal removed, side view H flower buds on trunk. A-E, H Couvreur 1143 (type) F, G Couvreur 1126. Photos Thomas Couvreur." ;
